metadata.name: To Reach the Star
metadata.description:
This NFT represents the Original Canvas Painting I did in 2017. 

100x60 cm (39x24 inch)
Oil on canvas
2017

This painting is about the eternal female dissatisfaction in terms of desires. For example: she can fill up her closet and still have nothing to wear. Here in the picture the same topic is presented as a parallel with the parable of the donkey and the carrot. The star which the girl tries to touch, is tied to her lush hair. This is as impossible as gathering a reasonably satisfactory collection of shoes.

This picture needs to be looked at very closely because it is like a rebus, full of symbols and images. Which ones have revealed themselves to you?
